<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Vevsdesign — Svadobná Výzdoba</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  :root{
    --cream:#ffffff;--warm:#fdfaf6;--blush:#eee4d8;--blush-d:#b59a7b;
    --sage:#e8dccb;--dark:#43362c;--mid:#76695e;--light:#ab9d91;
    --gold:#c1a678;--gold-l:#dec9a7;--gold-d:#a3875d;--paper:#f7f1e8;
    --shadow:0 22px 50px rgba(92,74,53,0.06);
    --serif:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;--sans:'Jost',sans-serif;
  }
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{font-family:var(--sans);background:#ffffff;color:var(--dark);font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;overflow-x:hidden}

  /* NAV */
  nav{position:fixed;top:0;width:100%;z-index:100;padding:1rem 4rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(193,166,120,0.16)}
  .nav-logo-text{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--dark);text-decoration:none}
  .nav-logo-text span{color:var(--gold);font-style:italic}
  nav ul{list-style:none;display:flex;gap:2.5rem}
  nav a{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:0.74rem;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mid);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.3s}
  nav a:hover{color:var(--gold)}

  /* HERO */
  #hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;text-align:center;padding:9rem 2rem 5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:#fff}
  .hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:0;background:transparent}
  
  /* BIG WATERMARK LOGO */
  .hero-watermark{display:none}
  .hero-watermark-clean{
    position:absolute;
    top:58%;left:52%;
    transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
    width:min(1280px, 118vw);
    height:auto;
    z-index:1;
    opacity:0.18;
    mix-blend-mode:multiply;
    filter:none;
    pointer-events:none;
    user-select:none;
  }
  
  .petal{position:absolute;border-radius:50% 0 50% 0;opacity:0.015;filter:blur(14px)}
  .p1{width:320px;height:320px;background:var(--blush);top:8%;left:3%;transform:rotate(28deg)}
  .p2{width:200px;height:200px;background:var(--gold-l);top:55%;right:5%;transform:rotate(-18deg)}
  .p3{width:140px;height:140px;background:var(--gold);bottom:12%;left:12%;transform:rotate(52deg)}
  
  .hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:720px;animation:fadeUp 1.2s ease both}
  .hero-tag{position:relative;top:-7.4rem;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:-1.4rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:1rem}
  .hero-tag::before,.hero-tag::after{content:'';display:block;width:45px;height:0.5px;background:var(--gold)}
  h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2.8rem,7vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.1;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:1.4rem}
  h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--blush-d)}
  .hero-sub{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.14rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--mid);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;letter-spacing:0.02em}
  .btn-pair{display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .btn-p{padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;background:var(--dark);color:var(--warm);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:0.76rem;letter-spacing:0.13em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.3s,transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.3s;box-shadow:0 18px 35px rgba(84,58,31,0.12)}
  .btn-p:hover{background:var(--mid);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 24px 40px rgba(84,58,31,0.16)}
  .btn-o{padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;background:rgba(255,248,239,0.55);color:var(--mid);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:0.76rem;letter-spacing:0.13em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border:0.5px solid rgba(191,154,125,0.55);transition:border-color 0.3s,color 0.3s,background 0.3s}
  .btn-o:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)}

  /* SECTIONS */
  section{padding:6rem 4rem}
  .sec-tag{font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--light);margin-bottom:0.6rem;text-align:center}
  h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:300;text-align:center;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:0.9rem}
  h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--blush-d)}
  .sec-intro{text-align:center;color:var(--mid);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 3.5rem;font-size:0.93rem}

  /* ABOUT */
  #about{background:rgba(253,250,246,0.7)}
  .about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;align-items:center}
  .about-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d9c2a2 0%,#c3a078 100%);border-radius:24px;padding:3rem 2.5rem;overflow:hidden;position:relative;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .about-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-30%;right:-20%;width:70%;aspect-ratio:1;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:50%}
  .about-card-q{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:300;color:white;font-style:italic;line-height:1.3}
  .about-card-sub{font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin-top:1rem}
  .accent-box{position:absolute;bottom:-1.5rem;right:-1.5rem;width:55%;aspect-ratio:1;background:var(--gold-l);opacity:0.18;border-radius:24px;z-index:-1}
  .about-text h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:1.2rem;line-height:1.3}
  .about-text p{color:var(--mid);margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:0.93rem}
  .about-stats{display:flex;gap:2.5rem;margin-top:2rem;padding-top:2rem;border-top:0.5px solid var(--gold-l)}
  .stat-n{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:2rem;font-weight:400;color:var(--dark)}
  .stat-l{font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--light)}

  /* DOPLNKOVE */
  #services{background:transparent;padding-top:2rem}
  .doplnkove-wrap{max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;border:0.5px solid rgba(193,166,120,0.16);background:rgba(253,250,246,0.92);padding:3rem 3.5rem;position:relative;border-radius:28px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .doplnkove-wrap::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-5px;left:-5px;right:-5px;bottom:-5px;border:0.5px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);pointer-events:none}
  .doplnkove-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.6rem;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-d);margin-bottom:1.8rem;text-align:center}
  .doplnkove-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:0.8rem 2rem}
  .doplnkove-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:0.6rem;font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--mid);padding:0.4rem 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15)}
  .doplnkove-item::before{content:'✓';color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:0.1rem;flex-shrink:0}
  .price-note{text-align:center;margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:0.5px solid var(--gold-l);font-size:1rem;color:var(--dark);font-style:italic;font-family:var(--serif)}

  /* BALIKY */
  #baliky{background:transparent;padding:6rem 4rem 2.25rem}
  #baliky .sec-tag{color:var(--gold-d);opacity:0.78}
  .baliky-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.25rem;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto}
  .balik-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);padding:2.5rem 2rem;transition:background 0.3s,transform 0.3s,box-shadow 0.3s,border-color 0.3s;position:relative;border:1px solid rgba(193,166,120,0.14);border-radius:28px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);cursor:pointer}
  .balik-card:hover{background:rgba(253,250,246,0.98);transform:translateY(-4px);border-color:rgba(193,166,120,0.3)}
  .balik-card:focus-visible{outline:none;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(193,166,120,0.22),var(--shadow)}
  .balik-card.featured{background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.98) 0%,rgba(248,242,234,0.96) 100%);border:1px solid rgba(193,166,120,0.22)}
  .balik-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,169,110,0.12);padding:0.3rem 0.8rem;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .balik-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:2rem;font-weight:300;font-style:italic;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:0.3rem}
  .balik-price{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.5rem;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .balik-list{list-style:none}
  .balik-list li{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--mid);padding:0.45rem 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.12);display:flex;gap:0.6rem}
  .balik-list li::before{content:'✓';color:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0}
  .balik-cta-hint{margin-top:1.3rem;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--light)}
  .baliky-note{text-align:center;max-width:820px;margin:2rem auto 0;color:var(--light);font-size:1.18rem;font-style:italic;font-family:var(--serif)}
  .balik-modal{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:250;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:2rem}
  .balik-modal[hidden]{display:none}
  .balik-modal-backdrop{position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(67,54,44,0.45);backdrop-filter:blur(6px)}
  .balik-modal-dialog{position:relative;z-index:1;width:min(760px,100%);max-height:min(88vh,900px);overflow:auto;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.98) 0%,rgba(251,247,241,0.98) 100%);border:1px solid rgba(193,166,120,0.22);border-radius:32px;box-shadow:0 30px 70px rgba(67,54,44,0.18);padding:2.6rem}
  .balik-modal-close{position:absolute;top:1rem;right:1rem;width:42px;height:42px;border:none;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(193,166,120,0.14);color:var(--dark);font-size:1.4rem;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.3s,color 0.3s}
  .balik-modal-close:hover{background:rgba(193,166,120,0.24);color:var(--gold-d)}
  .balik-modal-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,169,110,0.12);padding:0.35rem 0.85rem;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .balik-modal-head{padding-right:3rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .balik-modal-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.3rem);font-weight:300;font-style:italic;line-height:1.05;color:var(--dark)}
  .balik-modal-price{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.55rem;color:var(--gold);margin-top:0.4rem}
  .balik-modal-lead{color:var(--mid);font-size:0.98rem;max-width:620px;margin-bottom:1.6rem}
  .balik-modal-body{display:grid;gap:1.5rem}
  .balik-modal-section{padding:1.35rem 1.4rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.74);border:1px solid rgba(193,166,120,0.14);border-radius:22px}
  .balik-modal-section h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.35rem;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:0.7rem}
  .balik-modal-section p{color:var(--mid);font-size:0.92rem}
  .balik-modal-list{list-style:none}
  .balik-modal-list li{display:flex;gap:0.7rem;color:var(--mid);padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.12)}
  .balik-modal-list li:last-child{border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0}
  .balik-modal-list li::before{content:'✓';color:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0}
  .balik-modal-actions{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin-top:1.7rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:0.5px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.18)}
  .balik-modal-note{color:var(--light);font-size:0.82rem}
  body.modal-open{overflow:hidden}

  /* GALERIA */
  #galeria{background:rgba(253,250,246,0.64);padding:6rem 4rem}
  .gallery-placeholder-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1rem;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto}
  .gal-item{background:var(--blush);aspect-ratio:4/3;border-radius:1px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;cursor:pointer;transition:transform 0.3s}
  .gal-item:hover{transform:scale(1.02)}
  .gal-item:first-child{grid-column:span 2;aspect-ratio:2/1}
  .gal-item:nth-child(5){grid-column:span 2;aspect-ratio:2/1}
  .gal-img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform 0.4s}
  .gal-item:hover .gal-img{transform:scale(1.04)}
  .gal-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(201,169,110,0);transition:background 0.3s}
  .gal-item:hover .gal-overlay{background:rgba(201,169,110,0.1)}
  .gallery-note{text-align:center;margin-top:2.5rem;font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;color:var(--light);font-size:0.95rem}

  /* KONTAKT */
  #kontakt{background:transparent}
  .kontakt-wrap{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.94);border:0.5px solid rgba(193,166,120,0.16);padding:3.5rem;position:relative;border-radius:28px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .kontakt-wrap::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-5px;left:-5px;right:-5px;bottom:-5px;border:0.5px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);pointer-events:none}
  .kontakt-person{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;padding-bottom:2rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--gold-l)}
  .kontakt-avatar{width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#d4bea3,#bc9f76);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.4rem;color:white;flex-shrink:0}
  .kontakt-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:400}
  .kontakt-role{font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--light)}
  .kontakt-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.5rem 2rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem}
  .kontakt-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.2rem}
  .k-label{font-size:0.67rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--light)}
  .k-val{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--dark)}
  .k-val a{color:var(--dark);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.3s}
  .k-val a:hover{color:var(--gold)}
  .form-group{margin-bottom:1.1rem}
  .form-group label{display:block;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--light);margin-bottom:0.35rem}
  .form-group input,.form-group textarea,.form-group select{width:100%;padding:0.75rem 1rem;background:rgba(253,250,246,0.98);border:0.5px solid var(--gold-l);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--dark);outline:none;transition:border-color 0.3s,background 0.3s;appearance:none;border-radius:16px}
  .form-group input:focus,.form-group textarea:focus,.form-group select:focus{border-color:var(--gold)}
  .form-group textarea{height:110px;resize:vertical}
  .form-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem}
  .btn-submit{width:100%;padding:1rem;background:var(--dark);color:var(--warm);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:0.76rem;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.3s,box-shadow 0.3s;border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 18px 32px rgba(84,58,31,0.12)}
  .btn-submit:hover{background:var(--mid)}

  /* FOOTER */
  footer{background:rgba(253,250,246,0.96);color:var(--mid);padding:2.5rem 4rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-size:0.76rem;letter-spacing:0.05em;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(193,166,120,0.14)}
  .foot-brand{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.3rem;color:var(--dark)}
  .foot-brand span{color:var(--gold);font-style:italic}
  .foot-social{display:flex;gap:1.5rem}
  .foot-social a{color:var(--mid);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;transition:color 0.3s}
  .foot-social a:hover{color:var(--gold)}

  @keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

  @media(max-width:768px){
    nav{padding:1rem 1.5rem}
    nav ul{display:none}
    section{padding:4rem 1.5rem}
    #baliky{padding:4rem 1.5rem 1.5rem}
    #services{padding-top:1.5rem}
    #galeria{padding:4rem 1.5rem}
    .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2rem}
    .doplnkove-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    .baliky-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .gallery-placeholder-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    .gal-item:first-child,.gal-item:nth-child(5){grid-column:span 2;aspect-ratio:16/9}
    .kontakt-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .form-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .kontakt-wrap{padding:2rem 1.5rem}
    .doplnkove-wrap{padding:2rem 1.5rem}
    footer{flex-direction:column;text-align:center;padding:2rem 1.5rem}
    .hero-watermark-clean{top:61%;left:51%;width:120vw}
    .balik-modal{padding:1rem}
    .balik-modal-dialog{padding:1.6rem 1.2rem 1.4rem}
    .balik-modal-actions{flex-direction:column;align-items:stretch}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <span class="nav-logo-text">Vevs<span>design</span></span>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#about">O nás</a></li>
    <li><a href="#baliky">Balíky</a></li>
    <li><a href="#services">Služby</a></li>
    <li><a href="#kontakt">Kontakt</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <div class="petal p1"></div>
    <div class="petal p2"></div>
    <div class="petal p3"></div>
  </div>
  <!-- BIG WATERMARK LOGO -->
  <img src="Feminine Floral wedding studio logo.png" alt="" class="hero-watermark-clean" aria-hidden="true">
  <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="" class="hero-watermark" aria-hidden="true">

  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-tag">Svadobná výzdoba &amp; dizajn</div>
    <h1>Váš deň, <em>dokonale</em> zariadený</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Tvoríme svadobné atmosféry plné krásy a detailov.</p>
    <div class="btn-pair">
      <a href="#kontakt" class="btn-p">Napíšte nám</a>
      <a href="#baliky" class="btn-o">Naše balíky</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <p class="sec-tag">Kto sme</p>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div style="position:relative">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:300;color:white;font-style:italic;line-height:1.3">„Detaily robia svadbu nezabudnuteľnou."</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin-top:1rem">Vevsdesign · Košice &amp; východné Slovensko</div>
      </div>
      <div class="accent-box"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <h3>Vaša svadba, naša vášeň</h3>
      <p>Kreativita je našou silnou stránkou a veríme, že práve detaily robia svadbu nezabudnuteľnou. Vašu svadbu nevnímame ako zákazku, ale ako jedinečný príbeh, pri ktorom záleží na každom prvku, každej emócii aj na atmosfére, ktorú spolu vytvárame. Naším cieľom je, aby si hostia aj po rokoch povedali: „Táto svadba bola úžasná.“ Všetko tvoríme srdcom a s dôrazom na to, aby bol váš deň výnimočný presne tak, ako vy.</p>
      <div class="about-stats">
        <div><div class="stat-n">Desiatky+</div><div class="stat-l">Návrhov</div></div>
        <div><div class="stat-n">3</div><div class="stat-l">Hlavné balíky</div></div>
        <div><div class="stat-n">Individuálne</div><div class="stat-l">Balíky návrhov</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="baliky" style="background:transparent;padding:6rem 4rem">
  <h2 style="color:var(--dark)">Naše <em style="color:var(--gold)">balíky</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-intro" style="color:var(--mid)">Vyberte si balík, ktorý vám najlepšie vyhovuje, alebo si ho vyskladajte na mieru.</p>
  <div class="baliky-grid">
